name: Buma Gana
about: Hi! I'm Buma and I'm a junior ('22) studying information science and an aspiring product designer. I'm really passionate about augumented/virtual reality, tech for social impact and accessible design education. On campus I'm a part of The Wardrobe, Cornell Panhellenic, Medium Design Collective. Outside of school I'm really interested in astrology, fashion and watching funny tiktok threads on youtube!
